{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/como-melhorar-formularios-usando-input-mode/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Ramblings","author":"Ivan Bila"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"10d458b7-7fcc-5d63-a327-bf5a613eb1cd","excerpt":"Um dos componentes mais usados/comuns em diversas aplicações Web é o  e este pode ser usado\npara diversas finalidades sendo a principal capturar informação…","html":"<p>Um dos componentes mais usados/comuns em diversas aplicações Web é o <code class=\"language-text\">form</code> e este pode ser usado\npara diversas finalidades sendo a principal capturar informação sobre o utilizador ou uma determinada entidade.</p>\n<p>Um formulário pode ser composto por checkboxes, radiobuttons e <code class=\"language-text\">input[type=&quot;text&quot;]</code> e outros componentes/elementos usados\npara capturar dados com a melhor experiência de utilizador possível.</p>\n<p>Dado que a forma em que o formulário se apresenta pode influenciar significativamente a experiência dos utilizadores\né sempre importante escolher o elemento/componente adequado para este feito, tendo em conta acessibilidade e usabilidade.</p>\n<p>Antes da criação do atributo <code class=\"language-text\">inputmode</code> para formulários mais especificamente para o elemento <code class=\"language-text\">input</code> não era possível\ndeterminar o comportamento do teclado de um smartphone sendo que esta funcionalidade estava disponcccvel apenas para aplicações\nnativas.</p>\n<p>Actualmente a realidade é diferente e é possivel definir o comportamento de teclado, com isso podemos escolher se o teclado\napresenta somente numeros, letras, @, numeros com vírgula e muito mais, usando o attributo <code class=\"language-text\">inputmode</code> com os valores <em>decimal</em>, <em>numeric</em>, <em>tel</em>, <em>search</em>, <em>email</em> e <em>url</em>.</p>\n<h3>Inputmode decimal</h3>\n<p>Atraves do <code class=\"language-text\">inputmode=&quot;decimal&quot;</code> podemos instruir o teclado a mostrar somente numeros, como mostra a imagem e o campo de texto(somente disponível para smartphones com navegador elegível) abaixo. </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">inputmode</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>decimal<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Decimal<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7eaaef22c0d207f9e00fd9a4d70f1299/b8ccf/decimal.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 126.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Input mode decimal image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7eaaef22c0d207f9e00fd9a4d70f1299/799d3/decimal.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7eaaef22c0d207f9e00fd9a4d70f1299/00d96/decimal.png 148w,\n/static/7eaaef22c0d207f9e00fd9a4d70f1299/0b23c/decimal.png 295w,\n/static/7eaaef22c0d207f9e00fd9a4d70f1299/799d3/decimal.png 590w,\n/static/7eaaef22c0d207f9e00fd9a4d70f1299/b8ccf/decimal.png 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<center>\n\t<input type=\"text\" inputmode=\"decimal\" placeholder=\"Decimal\" class=\"inputmode\" style=\"padding: 10px; margin: 40px\"/>\n</center>\n<h3>Numeric</h3>\n<p>Diferentemente do decimal o <code class=\"language-text\">inputmode=&quot;numeric&quot;</code> apresenta somente números sem vírgula ou ponto, este pode\nser util para capturar dados como PIN, numero de itens a comprar, número de casa e mais outros dados, e comporta-se da seguinte maneira:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">inputmode</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>numeric<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>numeric<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/95095b5c410488c8aa889df52500faec/b8ccf/numeric.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 128.13333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Input mode numeric image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/95095b5c410488c8aa889df52500faec/799d3/numeric.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/95095b5c410488c8aa889df52500faec/00d96/numeric.png 148w,\n/static/95095b5c410488c8aa889df52500faec/0b23c/numeric.png 295w,\n/static/95095b5c410488c8aa889df52500faec/799d3/numeric.png 590w,\n/static/95095b5c410488c8aa889df52500faec/b8ccf/numeric.png 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<center>\n\t<input type=\"text\" inputmode=\"numeric\" placeholder=\"numeric\" class=\"inputmode\" style=\"padding: 10px; margin: 40px\"/>\n</center>\n<h3>Tel</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">inputmode=&quot;tel&quot;</code> apresenta algumas semelhanças comparado ao <code class=\"language-text\">numeric</code>, as únicas diferença são os símbolos\n<code class=\"language-text\">+*#</code> que são específicos de números de telefone, o teclado apresenta-se da seguinte maneira:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">inputmode</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>tel<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>tel<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8e340041d4a7d6003b1569d7915b1a1a/b8ccf/tel.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 128.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Input mode tel image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8e340041d4a7d6003b1569d7915b1a1a/799d3/tel.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8e340041d4a7d6003b1569d7915b1a1a/00d96/tel.png 148w,\n/static/8e340041d4a7d6003b1569d7915b1a1a/0b23c/tel.png 295w,\n/static/8e340041d4a7d6003b1569d7915b1a1a/799d3/tel.png 590w,\n/static/8e340041d4a7d6003b1569d7915b1a1a/b8ccf/tel.png 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<center>\n\t<input type=\"text\" inputmode=\"tel\" placeholder=\"tel\" class=\"inputmode\" style=\"padding: 10px; margin: 40px\"/>\n</center>\n<h3>Search</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">inputmode=&quot;search&quot;</code> altera somente o botão enter/return pelo go/ir, dado que enter/return podem servir para\nquebra de linha(dependendo do dispositivo/aplicção e das configurações), o teclado não foge muito da regra dos\nteclados disponíveis por padrão.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">inputmode</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>search<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>search<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/34d5e921a3df384ccc829b521beab020/b8ccf/search.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 134.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Input mode search image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/34d5e921a3df384ccc829b521beab020/799d3/search.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/34d5e921a3df384ccc829b521beab020/00d96/search.png 148w,\n/static/34d5e921a3df384ccc829b521beab020/0b23c/search.png 295w,\n/static/34d5e921a3df384ccc829b521beab020/799d3/search.png 590w,\n/static/34d5e921a3df384ccc829b521beab020/b8ccf/search.png 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<center>\n\t<input type=\"text\" inputmode=\"search\" placeholder=\"search\" class=\"inputmode\" style=\"padding: 10px; margin: 40px\"/>\n</center>\n<h3>Email</h3>\n<p>Através do <code class=\"language-text\">inputmode=&quot;email&quot;</code> o teclado inclui @ e dependendo do dispositivo/teclado padrão até dominíos de alguns emails comuns,\nno IOS13(Safari) o teclado sugere um email do utilizador, e apresenta-se da seguinte maneira:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">inputmode</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>email<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Email<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c56da18d27d4c6913117e8f4fc176b4c/b8ccf/email.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 137.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Input mode search email\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c56da18d27d4c6913117e8f4fc176b4c/799d3/email.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c56da18d27d4c6913117e8f4fc176b4c/00d96/email.png 148w,\n/static/c56da18d27d4c6913117e8f4fc176b4c/0b23c/email.png 295w,\n/static/c56da18d27d4c6913117e8f4fc176b4c/799d3/email.png 590w,\n/static/c56da18d27d4c6913117e8f4fc176b4c/b8ccf/email.png 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<center>\n\t<input type=\"text\" inputmode=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email\" class=\"inputmode\" style=\"padding: 10px; margin: 40px\"/>\n</center>\n<h3>Url</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">inputmode=&quot;url&quot;</code> é provavelmente a opção com menos casos de uso porém importante, com ele o teclado adiciona / e .com\n(dependendo do dispositivo ou teclado padra pode ate sugerir mais opções).</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">inputmode</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>url<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">placeholder</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Url<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6b4d4751b0e4f647d12ba4428739c347/b8ccf/url.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 133.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Input mode url\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6b4d4751b0e4f647d12ba4428739c347/799d3/url.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6b4d4751b0e4f647d12ba4428739c347/00d96/url.png 148w,\n/static/6b4d4751b0e4f647d12ba4428739c347/0b23c/url.png 295w,\n/static/6b4d4751b0e4f647d12ba4428739c347/799d3/url.png 590w,\n/static/6b4d4751b0e4f647d12ba4428739c347/b8ccf/url.png 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<center>\n\t<input type=\"text\" inputmode=\"url\" placeholder=\"Url\" class=\"inputmode\" style=\"padding: 10px; margin: 40px\"/>\n</center>\n<p>O <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#input-modalities:-the-inputmode-attribute\">inputmode</a> pode ser usado em textareas e para esconder o teclado com o valor <code class=\"language-text\">inputmode=&quot;none&quot;</code>.\nApesar de poder melhorar a experiência do utilizador ao apresentar diferentes modelos/layouts de teclado  o <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/inputmode\"><code class=\"language-text\">inputmode</code></a> ainda tem fraco <a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=input-inputmode\">supporte</a> funcionando em alguns navegadores modernos o que pode beneficiar apenas uma parte dos utilizadores.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Como melhorar formularios usando Input Mode","date":"December 24, 2019","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/como-melhorar-formularios-usando-input-mode/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/security-on-the-front-end/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Security on the Front-End"}},"next":null}}}